title: 07 - Your Pump Up for Today (Moments from IF 2020)
description:
IF 2021 is coming up on March 5-6th and we want you to be a part. These are just 3 of our favorite moments from IF 2020 from my friends Bianca Olthoff, Jada Edwards, and Sadie Robertson.

IF:Gathering is virtual this year and you can watch alone or with your people, learn more here: IFGATHERING2021.COM
